depot application using:

-Ruby 1.9.2-p180
-Rails (3.1.0-rc)
-Rspec (2.6.0)
-Cucumber (0.10.3)
-MongoDB
-Coffescript


WATCH OUT!!

#Creating a new rails app using mongodb:

>>rails new app -OJT 

-O, [--skip-activerecord]  # Skip Active Record files
-J, [--skip-prototype]     # Skip Prototype files
-T, [--skip-testunit]      # Skip Test::Unit files

>>cd app

>> rails generate mongo_mapper:config

...create config/mongo.ymlc

#End Creating a new rails app
